caption.p: The effects of fennel and TA treatment on the (a) MDA, (b) total thiol content, (c) SOD and (d) CAT activities in the liver tissues of the STZ‐induced diabetic rats ( n = 6). *** p < .001 shows the significant differences with the control group. # p < .05, ## p < .01, ### p < .001 shows the significant differences with the STZ group. +++ p < .001 shows the significant differences with the STZ + TA group
